\n                                                    <\/a>\n                                                                                                    <\/div>\n\n                                                \n                                                <div class=\"vip-mega-panel vip-mega-card\">\n                                                                                                        <a class=\"vip-mega-link\"\n                                                        href=\"\/ht\/ipotek\/pre-ipotek\">\n                                                        Pr\u00e8 ipot\u00e8k\n                                                    <\/a>\n                                                                                                    <\/div>\n                                            <\/div>\n\n                                        <\/div>\n                                                                            <\/div>\n                                <\/div>\n\n                            <\/div>\n                        <\/div>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/li>\n\n                <!-- Liens normaux -->\n                <li class=\"nav-item\"><a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"\/ht\/construction\">Ekip Nou an<\/a><\/li>\n                <li class=\"nav-item\"><a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"\/ht\/carrieres\">Kary\u00e8<\/a><\/li>\n                <li class=\"nav-item\"><a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"\/ht\/partenaires\">Patn\u00e8 yo<\/a><\/li>\n                <li class=\"nav-item\"><a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"\/ht\/contact\">Kontak<\/a><\/li>\n\n                <!-- CTA -->\n                <li class=\"nav-item ms-xl-2 my-3 my-xl-0\">\n                    <a href=\"\/ht\/contact\" class=\"btn vip-btn-gold rounded-pill px-4 py-2 w-100 w-xl-auto\">\n                        Konsiltasyon Gratis\n                    <\/a>\n                <\/li>\n\n                <!-- Mobile: lien Services simple -->\n                <li class=\"nav-item d-xl-none\">\n                    <a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"\/ht\/services\">S\u00e8vis yo<\/a>\n                <\/li>\n\n            <\/ul>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/nav>\r\n    \r\n    \n\n<section class=\"section-padding bg-white\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"row align-items-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-lg-6 mb-4 mb-lg-0\">\n                <h2 class=\"fw-bold mb-3\" style=\"color: var(--primary-color);\">Kisa yon asirans lavi ye?<\/h2>\n                <div style=\"width: 60px; height: 3px; background: var(--secondary-color); margin-bottom: 20px;\"><\/div>\n                <div class=\"text-muted text-justify\" style=\"line-height: 1.8;\">\n                    <p>Asirans lavi se yon kontra ant yon moun ki asire ak yon konpayi asirans ki f\u00e8t apre yo fin evalye pri a. Nan kontra sa a, asirans lan pwom\u00e8t pou l peye moun ou chwazi a (benefisy\u00e8 a) yon montan lajan al\u00f2ske ou menm ou peye prim ou yo regily\u00e8man.<br><br>Montan lajan sa a, yo rele l dedomajman pou lanm\u00f2 oswa kapital-lanm\u00f2, an jeneral li pa gen okenn taks sou li pou benefisy\u00e8 a. Gen de gwo kalite asirans lavi: <strong>tanpor\u00e8<\/strong> ak <strong>p\u00e8manan<\/strong>.<\/p>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"col-lg-6\">\n                <img src=\"https:\/\/vipgpi.net\/assets\/img\/assuranceVie\/A-cote-texte-assurance-vie-1.jpg\" alt=\"Kisa yon asirans lavi ye?\" class=\"img-fluid rounded shadow-lg\">\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n\n<section class=\"section-padding pb-0\" style=\"background-color: #f8f9fa;\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"text-center mb-5\">\n            <h3 class=\"fw-bold\" style=\"color: var(--primary-color);\">1. Asirans lavi Tanpor\u00e8<\/h3>\n            <p class=\"text-muted\">Yon solisyon fleksib pou bezwen ki gen yon tan fikse.<\/p>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n<section class=\"py-5 mb-5 d-flex align-items-center\" style=\"background-color: #0b0d26; width: 100%; border-radius: 0 200px 200px 0; min-height: 400px;\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"row g-4\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-4\">\n                <div class=\"card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm p-4 text-center bg-white rounded-4 hover-lift\">\n                    <div class=\"mb-3\">\n                        <img src=\"https:\/\/vipgpi.net\/assets\/img\/assuranceVie\/Protection-du-revenu.png\" alt=\"Dire ki Limite\" style=\"width: 70px; height: auto;\">\n                    <\/div>\n                    <h5 class=\"fw-bold\" style=\"color: var(--primary);\">Dire ki Limite<\/h5>\n                    <p class=\"small text-muted mb-0\">Asirans lavi tanpor\u00e8 a ba w pwoteksyon pou yon pery\u00f2d byen defini, ki ka soti nan 10 pou rive 40 an.<\/p>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n            <div class=\"col-md-4\">\n                <div class=\"card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm p-4 text-center bg-white rounded-4 hover-lift\">\n                    <div class=\"mb-3\">\n                        <img src=\"https:\/\/vipgpi.net\/assets\/img\/assuranceVie\/Paiement-des-dettes.png\" alt=\"Ou ka renouvle l\" style=\"width: 70px; height: auto;\">\n                    <\/div>\n                    <h5 class=\"fw-bold\" style=\"color: var(--primary);\">Ou ka renouvle l<\/h5>\n                    <p class=\"small text-muted mb-0\">L\u00e8 pery\u00f2d pwoteksyon an fini, ou ka renouvle kontra a, men souvan asirans lan ap vin pi ch\u00e8.<\/p>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n            <div class=\"col-md-4\">\n                <div class=\"card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm p-4 text-center bg-white rounded-4 hover-lift\">\n                    <div class=\"mb-3\">\n                        <img src=\"https:\/\/vipgpi.net\/assets\/img\/assuranceVie\/Securite-financiere.png\" alt=\"Ou ka chanje l (Konv\u00e8tib)\" style=\"width: 70px; height: auto;\">\n                    <\/div>\n                    <h5 class=\"fw-bold\" style=\"color: var(--primary);\">Ou ka chanje l (Konv\u00e8tib)<\/h5>\n                    <p class=\"small text-muted mb-0\">Ou ka chanje asirans tanpor\u00e8 a pou f\u00e8 l tounen yon asirans lavi p\u00e8manan san w pa bezwen pase nan okenn egzamen medikal.<\/p>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n\n<section class=\"section-padding pb-0\" style=\"background-color: #f8f9fa;\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"text-center mb-5\">\n            <h3 class=\"fw-bold\" style=\"color: var(--primary-color);\">2. Asirans lavi P\u00e8manan<\/h3>\n            <p class=\"text-muted\">Yon pwoteksyon pou tout lavi ak plizy\u00e8 avantaj finansye.<\/p>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n<section class=\"py-5 mb-5 d-flex align-items-center\" style=\"background-color: #0b0d26; width: 100%; border-radius: 200px 0 0 200px; min-height: 400px;\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"row g-4\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-4\">\n                <div class=\"card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm p-4 text-center bg-white rounded-4 hover-lift\">\n                    <div class=\"mb-3\">\n                        <img src=\"https:\/\/vipgpi.net\/assets\/img\/assuranceVie\/Protection-du-revenu.png\" alt=\"Dire ki pa Limite\" style=\"width: 70px; height: auto;\">\n                    <\/div>\n                    <h5 class=\"fw-bold\" style=\"color: var(--primary);\">Dire ki pa Limite<\/h5>\n                    <p class=\"small text-muted mb-0\">Asirans lavi p\u00e8manan an pwoteje w pou tout lavi w n\u00e8t.<\/p>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n            <div class=\"col-md-4\">\n                <div class=\"card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm p-4 text-center bg-white rounded-4 hover-lift\">\n                    <div class=\"mb-3\">\n                        <img src=\"https:\/\/vipgpi.net\/assets\/img\/assuranceVie\/Paiement-des-dettes.png\" alt=\"Val\u00e8 Racha (Valeur de rachat)\" style=\"width: 70px; height: auto;\">\n                    <\/div>\n                    <h5 class=\"fw-bold\" style=\"color: var(--primary);\">Val\u00e8 Racha (Valeur de rachat)<\/h5>\n                    <p class=\"small text-muted mb-0\">Ou ka f\u00e8 prete k\u00f2b sou val\u00e8 lajan ki akimile nan kontra a oswa ou ka rale l.<\/p>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n            <div class=\"col-md-4\">\n                <div class=\"card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm p-4 text-center bg-white rounded-4 hover-lift\">\n                    <div class=\"mb-3\">\n                        <img src=\"https:\/\/vipgpi.net\/assets\/img\/assuranceVie\/Securite-financiere.png\" alt=\"Envestisman\" style=\"width: 70px; height: auto;\">\n                    <\/div>\n                    <h5 class=\"fw-bold\" style=\"color: var(--primary);\">Envestisman<\/h5>\n                    <p class=\"small text-muted mb-0\">Gen k\u00e8k kontra ki gen yon pati ladan l ki la pou envestisman epi ki bay dividann.<\/p>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n\n<section class=\"section-padding bg-primary\" style=\"background-color: var(--primary) !important;\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"text-center mb-5\">\n            <h2 class=\"fw-bold text-white\">Opsyon pou w Enskri<\/h2>\n            <p class=\"text-white-50\">Konprann diferans ant asirans ki mande egzamen medikal ak sa ki pa mande l yo.<\/p>\n        <\/div>\n\n        <div class=\"row g-4\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-6\">\n                <div class=\"p-4 rounded h-100 bg-white shadow-lg border-0 hover-lift\">\n                    <div class=\"d-flex align-items-center mb-3\">\n                        <i class=\"fas fa-stethoscope fa-2x me-3\" style=\"color: var(--secondary);\"><\/i>\n                        <h4 class=\"mb-0 fw-bold\" style=\"color: va